channel.title: [PI] Project Insanity: Preloading Models
channel.description:
How To PreLoad Models!
Lets Begin,
In your Client folder open up Client.java and search for
[code]//preloadModels();[/code]
And delete the // so it looks like this [code]preloadModels();[/code] Save and exit Client.java Now that we have made it preload we will need it to preload to a specific folder, that is easy! In your Client folder still, make a new folder called 'Raw' and rememeber, without the quotations!
I hope you liked my tutorial/snippet.
